        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #d4a254; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Go Deeper Into Election</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
            <a href="/question-chosen" style="display: block; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(212,162,84,0.15); border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                <div style="color: #d4a254; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">The Evidence</div>
