                <div style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.3rem;">Ephesians 1:3-11 — the Scripture passage that frames everything</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/devotional-adoption-papers" style="display: block; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(212,162,84,0.15); border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                <div style="color: #d4a254; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;">Devotional</div>
                <div style="color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600;">Your Adoption Papers Were Signed Before You Existed</div>
                <div style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.3rem;">5-minute meditation on irrevocable grace</div>
